name: How to Play Pinball
description: Come learn tips and tricks to maximize your understanding (and your score) at pinball

name: Flippin' Friday Kickoff Dinner
description: Join us for dinner onsite in a private, casual setting with many of this year's Pinlebrities and Speakers. \n\n Tickets may still be available!

name: Sparky's BBQ
description: Come join us for a potluck BBQ with you pinball friends!

name: John Osborne's Topic
description: He is going to do something?!?!?!

name: JJP Autograph Session
description: Come get autographs from the owners of Jersey Jack Pinball, makers of Dialed In, Wizard of Oz, The Hobbit, and Pirates of the Carribean

name: Pinball Raffle
description: GSPF is raffling off items including a pinball machine! Get your tickets while you can!

name: Stern Pinball Discussion
description: Mike and Tanio work at Stern Pinball - Mike does software testing, rule design, and runs the field test program. Tanio Klyce was part of the design team for Deadpool, Kiss, and Star Trek. Come and listen to them speak!

name: Donnie Gillies Autographs
description: Deemed to be one of the most influential artists to invade the pop culture scenes of the punk, rock n roll and heavy metal underground, Dirty Donny has been spreading his art across all mediums for decades; ranging from skate decks to pinball machines, hot rods and album covers to name but a few.

name: Closing Time!
description: You don't have to go home, but you can't stay here. See you Sunday!
